PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of KATHRYN E. McCALLION, of Ottawa, Ontario, in the place of Marc A. Brault, who has resigned, and JOHN M. BANIGAN, of Ottawa, Ontario, in the place of Alan B. Nymark, who has resigned, as directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years.
